1
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,079
Yang Liu ran off with the gift money

2
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:38,880
What

3
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,439
Mom

4
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:42,640
That woman said

5
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:45,640
She knows our family borrowed money to get married

6
00:00:46,039 --> 00:00:47,320
She said our family committed marriage fraud

7
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,200
So she took the money

8
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:49,600
Said the money is compensation for emotional distress

9
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:52,520
This wretched woman

10
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,880
Go find Yang Liu and bring her back to me

11
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:58,039
Seductress

12
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,079
Wang Shulan

13
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:02,399
You shameless thing

14
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,120
My family's happy occasion

15
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:05,920
Was turned into chaos by you

16
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,560
Your family has to compensate me

17
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,719
Chen Xuelin

18
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:10,319
You're blaming the victim

19
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,239
It's one thing that you usually throw tantrums and bully me

20
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:14,760
But you dare to harm my child

21
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,359
It was all delayed by you people

22
00:01:16,359 --> 00:01:18,359
Caused our Sweetheart to suffer

23
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,959
It's all your fault

24
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:20,879
You still blame me

25
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,200
If it weren't for you people

26
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,920
Delaying our auspicious time

27
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,879
And making the wedding car drive backwards

28
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,640
You reversed all the good luck away

29
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,519
Caused my daughter-in-law to run away too

30
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,560
The gift money is gone too

31
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,280
Your Wang family must compensate me for my daughter-in-law

32
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,280
Compensate me for the gift money

33
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,920
Is there anyone as unreasonable as you

34
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:37,079
You married a thieving wife yourself

35
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:38,239
Why blame us

36
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,120
Mom

37
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,000
Let's go back

38
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,359
You

39
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:42,920
Mom

40
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,319
Stop making a scene

41
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,000
Finding Yang Liu is the priority now

42
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:47,680
Pfft

43
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,760
I'll settle the score with you when I get back

44
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:50,920
Let's go

45
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,599
I think that girl

46
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,920
Saw through that evil mother-in-law's true colors

47
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,879
Ran back in the dead of night

48
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,439
She even talks about distant relatives not being as good as neighbors

49
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:07,079
I think that whole family

50
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,360
Are all evil neighbors and mad dogs

51
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,400
Dying to take a bite out of us

52
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,479
No

53
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,039
What are you chopping

54
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,280
Chopping an enemy

55
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,280
I am chopping an enemy

56
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,840
She must have left by car

57
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:29,000
Can't find anyone now

58
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,319
Mom

59
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,319
What are you going to do

60
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:34,159
Go find the Wang family, of course

61
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,879
I get angry just thinking about it

62
00:02:36,879 --> 00:02:37,960
A perfectly good wedding

63
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,240
Was ruined by them

64
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,400
If they hadn't jinxed the wedding

65
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,560
Why would Yang Liu leave

66
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:44,560
I can't swallow this anger

67
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,960
Mom is right

68
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,560
We should go ask that shrew for money

69
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:47,960
She caused me

70
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,400
Number Three

71
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:49,599
Shut up

72
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:52,719
Mom

73
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,960
I was careless about this matter

74
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,639
That Yang Liu is a marriage fraudster

75
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,879
Didn't you see that matchmaker Yang

76
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,800
Ran away too

77
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:02,360
That person didn't genuinely want to live with me anyway

78
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,800
So don't go making a scene

79
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,680
Are you speaking for outsiders

80
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:07,120
I think your heart

81
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,360
Has been hooked away by that neighbor

82
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,960
Seductress

83
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,879
That Number Two

84
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,319
Just like her mother when she was young

85
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:13,680
A born Seductress

86
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,520
Mom

87
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,120
Who am I

88
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:20,759
Which handsome guy for miles around doesn't know

89
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,879
There are plenty of girls who want to be with me

90
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,599
When would it be her turn

91
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,800
Not interested

92
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,439
You're not interested in her

93
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,479
You even backed the car for her

94
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,280
I saw it all

95
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,719
Mom

96
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,800
Drink some water to cool down

97
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,560
Old Zheng, look at this.

98
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,960
If you hadn't swapped shifts with the Wang family back then,

99
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,039
you wouldn't have died.

100
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,240
Look, your son is still speaking up for the Wang family.

101
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,800
You might as well have taken me with you.

102
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,919
Just ask Dad to take me away with him then.

103
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,120
You want to go with your dad, is that it?

104
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,400
You, being the eldest,

105
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,120
don't care about your mom at all.

106
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,840
Raising the three of you all by myself,

107
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,319
do you know how hard it was?

108
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:02,520
And you still say things like that to upset me.

109
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,960
Mom, don't hit Big Brother.

110
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,520
Let me have some peace.

111
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,120
I can't calm down!

112
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,400
The money for your wedding,

113
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:13,080
I swallowed my pride to borrow it from others.

114
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,599
If I don't go to the Wang family,

115
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:17,240
who can I get the money from to pay them back?

116
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,439
Fine, fine, fine.

117
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,040
I'll go to the Wang family.

118
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,519
I'll go find them, okay?

119
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,879
My chicken soup!

120
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:52,040
Zheng Minjiang, what are you doing?

121
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,920
This is the chicken soup I stewed for my sister.

122
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,079
Do you really not want my sister to get better?

123
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:57,959
What are you talking about?

124
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:23,959
You just don't want my sister

125
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:25,519
to have this soup, is that it?

126
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,240
I...

127
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,439
What is it with you?

128
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,680
You want to be a Mama's boy again,

129
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,839
and come collect debt for your mom?

130
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:34,439
Zheng Minjiang.

131
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,120
Do you just do whatever your mom says?

132
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,839
Do you have eyes of your own?

133
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,439
Can't you tell right from wrong?

134
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:42,480
Your Zheng family borrowed money to get a wife,

135
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,879
the wife took the money and ran.

136
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:46,000
What gives you the right to come to my house demanding money?

137
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,000
I just think that some things

138
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:54,519
can be discussed, you know.

139
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,560
You...

140
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,720
I haven't finished speaking yet!

141
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,680
Stop right there.

142
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:09,399
Do you know

143
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,240
why my sister came back yesterday?

144
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,079
Because she wanted to give you a wedding gift.

145
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,399
And you?

146
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,680
What did you do?

147
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:18,519
Because my sister's treatment was delayed,

148
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,439
she had a massive hemorrhage.

149
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,839
She was in critical danger.

150
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,279
Does this have absolutely nothing

151
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:24,600
to do with your Zheng family?

152
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:26,120
Your sister...

153
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,800
I didn't know she would be like that.

154
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,759
I came over just to ask about

155
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:36,160
Yingzhu's condition.

156
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,560
Now you think of my sister?

157
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,920
Forget it.

158
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,879
And to think that before,

159
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,279
I thought your feelings for my sister were real.

160
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:45,319
Now it seems,

161
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:47,759
you're just a wolf in sheep's clothing.

162
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:49,920
What feelings do I have for her?

163
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,240
Let go.

164
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:51,800
No, wait.

165
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:53,720
What nonsense are you talking about?

166
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,680
If you're going to spout nonsense like this,

167
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:59,199
then let's just assume everything

168
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,319
is the Zheng family's fault.

169
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,720
And today, I owe the Wang family too.

170
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,199
Happy now?

171
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,480
Seriously.

172
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:07,439
You're like a fighting cock every day.

173
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,079
I can't be bothered to waste words with you.

174
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,680
You're sick

175
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:35,560
Provinces are transferring outstanding cadres to mountain areas

176
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,519
Manager! Manager!

177
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,199
Manager!

178
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:40,079
Suspending me?

179
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:41,600
Why?

180
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:44,040
I'm a factory activist every year

181
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,600
What did I do wrong at work?

182
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:47,199
Since there are no mistakes in your work...

183
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,680
...then it must be improper conduct

184
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:49,720
You...

185
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,040
...should think it over carefully

186
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:51,959
If you have nothing to do...

187
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,720
...why do you keep running to Director Zhang's?

188
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,720
What for?

189
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,800
Do I want to run to his office every day?

190
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,079
He's the one making up reasons to call me over

191
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,680
Yingrong

192
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,079
Some things...

193
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,959
...we don't need to spell out so clearly

194
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,519
Just listen to me

195
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,319
During your suspension...

196
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,680
...reflect on yourself properly

197
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:09,319
Why should I reflect?

198
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,000
That's just how it is

199
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:10,879
Stop talking

200
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,720
Minjiang

201
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,160
When you came to me about your wedding...

202
00:08:22,399 --> 00:08:23,680
...I told you then...

203
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,279
...the factory isn't doing well

204
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,639
The request you made...

205
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,160
...is very hard for me to handle

206
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,720
Director Wu

207
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:32,600
I haven't received my wages for three months

208
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,120
It's only right that I come to you for my wages

209
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,840
I know it's difficult for you

210
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,720
But the factory is state property

211
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,279
Paying wages isn't something I alone...

212
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,200
...have the final say on

213
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,120
How about this?

214
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,960
You write an application

215
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,960
I'll submit it for you

216
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,600
Fine

217
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:50,519
Since you can't solve the problem...

218
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,120
...I'll go ask the factory manager

219
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:55,679
Aren't you blowing this out of proportion?

220
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,840
If you give up...

221
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,320
...the competition for workshop maintenance director...

222
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,679
...I can apply for a sum of money for you

223
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,840
So Director Wu holding back my wages...

224
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,840
...was for this reason

225
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,399
But I'm rated excellent every year

226
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,759
Why should I give up the competition?

227
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,159
Hello?

228
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:29,679
Director Zhen.

229
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,679
I can't believe you called me.

230
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,679
Director Zhen.

231
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,559
Go ahead.

232
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,200
About Zheng Minjiang.

233
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:43,320
I want to transfer him to the province as a section chief.

234
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:46,080
When Minjiang came to the province to study,

235
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,320
I noticed him.

236
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,480
He has outstanding work ability.

237
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:51,240
And a steady personality.

238
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,960
I plan to

239
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:55,039
groom this promising talent properly.

240
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,799
It's like this.

241
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,799
Director Zhen.

242
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:02,679
Zheng Minjiang said he doesn't want to leave this factory.

243
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,080
Doesn't want to leave?

244
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,080
Why?

245
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,679
You might not know yet.

246
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:09,279
Zheng Minjiang just got married a couple of days ago.

247
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:10,840
They are newlyweds.

248
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,960
There's a pile of things at home

249
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,240
waiting for him to handle.

250
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,600
He can't get away.

251
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,240
So, in the end, they didn't sleep together, right?

252
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,720
The wife ran away in the middle of the night.

253
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,200
How could they sleep together?

254
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,639
Impossible.

255
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,720
Back to work just two days after the wedding.

256
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,159
So diligent.

257
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:34,480
Aren't you staying home with your wife?

258
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:36,759
Yeah, Minjiang.

259
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,919
You'd better keep an eye on your wife.

260
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,799
Is marriage fraud rare these days?

261
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,120
Let me tell you.

262
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,639
Just the night before last,

263
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,240
a new bride from a family

264
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,679
just got married

265
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,799
and ran away.

266
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,519
They didn't even see clearly who she was.

267
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:50,559
Tell me,

268
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:52,480
that unlucky guy,

269
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,519
spent a lot of money,

270
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,200
didn't consummate the marriage,

271
00:10:55,279 --> 00:10:56,960
it's so humiliating.

272
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,080
These tools are indeed handy.

273
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,879
What does this mean?

274
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,919
Don't mess around.

275
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:08,480
What are you doing?

276
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,480
Don't mess around.

277
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:11,799
Get over there.

278
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,039
What do you mean?

279
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:17,639
Coward.

280
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:31,960
Suspended from work.

281
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,799
If my mom finds out,

282
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:35,600
she'll tear the roof off.

283
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,679
Jobs are so hard to find.

284
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:41,320
Maybe I should brew vinegar like Second Aunt taught me.

285
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:43,159
But I have no manpower and no money.

286
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,320
I can't get it started right away.

287
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,519
I have to find a job quickly.

288
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:52,360
Hiring female machine operators.

289
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,879
Selling fish is good.

290
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,360
You can make money selling fish.

291
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,360
How about we partner up to catch and sell fish?

292
00:11:59,360 --> 00:11:59,919
How about it?

293
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,360
What you earn from selling fish

294
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,159
is way better than this salary.

295
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,159
This is an expert.

296
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:10,759
After long-term analysis and investigation,

297
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,360
the conclusion reached is...

298
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:15,559
Buying fish no longer requires fish coupons.

299
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,879
Chickens, ducks, and pigs aren't ready for market yet.

300
00:12:17,879 --> 00:12:19,600
Meat, eggs, and milk are in short supply.

301
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:21,960
People can only rely on eating fish for nutrition.

302
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,320
Besides,

303
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:26,840
the upstream dam is releasing water now.

304
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:29,320
It's a great opportunity to catch fish and make money.

305
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,919
Why don't

306
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:32,559
I sell some fish to pay off the debt?

307
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,320
If you don't believe me,

308
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,360
look there.

309
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:39,440
I want a grass carp.

310
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,639
Boss, four jin of crucian carp.

311
00:12:40,639 --> 00:12:41,399
Five jin, five jin.

312
00:12:41,559 --> 00:12:42,480
I want four grass carp.

313
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:42,919
See?

314
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:43,960
His fish

315
00:12:44,279 --> 00:12:45,759
are never enough to sell every day.

316
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:48,039
I need to go ask about his fish-raising secrets.

317
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,559
Queued for ages and didn't get a single one.

318
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:51,000
That person he mentioned

319
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:53,080
really is an expert.

320
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,279
Very good.

321
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,240
Extremely good.
